This repository provides a demo of how to
build a generic Twitter application based on
spark streaming.

It serves 3 purposes.

- Example of how to use spark streaming.
- Example of how to stream twitter data.
- Example of how to move data between spark streaming and cassandra.

The spark streaming application is implemented using
a generic framework, in the tweetstream package.

An example of the way that framework is used
is in the ctakes package.


